<header class="vc-page-head reveal">
  <div class="vc-page-eyebrow">Coalition · Application</div>
  <h1 class="vc-page-h">Apply to <em>the Coalition.</em></h1>
  <p class="vc-page-deck">The Coalition of the Willing is the network that powers the work. We coordinate — we do not absorb. Member organizations remain sovereign.</p>
</header>

<div class="apply-split reveal">

  <div class="apply-context">
    <span class="rubric">Why the Coalition</span>
    <h2>Built for those who are <em>already building.</em></h2>
    <p>The Coalition is not a membership club. It is a coordination layer for institutions, builders, and partners who are already doing the work — and who want to do more of it, faster, with less redundancy and more collective intelligence.</p>
    <p>E5 Enclave coordinates the research base, the data infrastructure, the agentic AI tools, and the institutional record. You bring your community, your expertise, and your mandate. Neither absorbs the other. The center holds.</p>

    <div class="apply-stats">
      <div class="apply-stat"><span class="n">1,247</span><span class="l">Supporters</span></div>
      <div class="apply-stat"><span class="n">38</span><span class="l">Member Orgs</span></div>
      <div class="apply-stat"><span class="n">5</span><span class="l">Pillars</span></div>
      <div class="apply-stat"><span class="n">50</span><span class="l">Cities Covered</span></div>
    </div>

    <span class="rubric" style="margin-top:32px;">The Four Tracks</span>
    <ul class="track-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Institutional Member</strong>
        Black-led organizations aligned with one or more pillars. Gain access to the collective research base, coordination network, and program partnership opportunities.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Individual Builder</strong>
        Researchers, technologists, organizers, and community practitioners contributing capacity to the pillars. Join the working network.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Partner Institution</strong>
        Universities, foundations, and aligned coalitions that amplify the work without governing it. Institutional sovereignty preserved.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Funder / Institutional Partner</strong>
        Foundations, DAFs, and institutional partners supporting programs. Full transparency into how resources are deployed.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <blockquote class="apply-quote">
      "E5 Enclave is building the evidence systems, the coordination infrastructure, and the institutional record that our communities have always needed. The Coalition is how we make it collective."
      <cite>Israel Lee Armstead · President &amp; CVO, E5 Enclave Incorporated</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>

  <div class="apply-form-col">
    <h3>Tell us what you <em>build.</em></h3>
    <p class="sub">A member of the Council will respond personally — usually within five business days. The center holds.</p>

    <form class="vc-form" data-vc-form data-subject="coalition-apply" data-endpoint="/api/contact" novalidate>
      <div class="field-row">
        <div class="row">
          <label for="apply-name">Name</label>
          <input id="apply-name" name="name" type="text" required autocomplete="name" placeholder="Your full name"/>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <label for="apply-org">Organization</label>
          <input id="apply-org" name="organization" type="text" autocomplete="organization" placeholder="Your org (if applicable)"/>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field-row">
        <div class="row">
          <label for="apply-email">Email</label>
          <input id="apply-email" name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email" placeholder="you@organization.org"/>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <label for="apply-role">Role / Title</label>
          <input id="apply-role" name="role" type="text" autocomplete="organization-title" placeholder="Director, Researcher, Builder…"/>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <label for="apply-track">Application Track</label>
        <select id="apply-track" name="track" required>
          <option value="">Select your track…</option>
          <option value="institutional">Institutional member (Black-led organization)</option>
          <option value="individual">Individual builder</option>
          <option value="partner">Partner institution / aligned coalition</option>
          <option value="funder">Funder / institutional partner</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <label for="apply-pillar">Primary pillar interest</label>
        <select id="apply-pillar" name="pillar">
          <option value="">No preference / multiple</option>
          <option value="economic">Economic — cooperative ownership &amp; credit access</option>
          <option value="environmental">Environmental — Lineage Farms · FarmBlock</option>
          <option value="educational">Educational — McCartney Academy</option>
          <option value="engagement">Engagement — Black Dragons Initiative</option>
          <option value="emancipated">Emancipated — Restitution 246</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <label for="apply-msg">What would you contribute, and what do you hope to gain?</label>
        <textarea id="apply-msg" name="message" required placeholder="Tell us about the work you steward, what you'd bring to the Coalition, and what coordination capacity would help you most."></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <button type="submit" class="vc-cta-primary" data-label="Submit application">Submit application <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></button>
        <span class="hint">Or email <a href="mailto:contact@e5enclave.com">contact@e5enclave.com</a></span>
      </div>
    </form>

    <div class="vc-form-success" role="status">
      <strong style="font-family:var(--vc-text); font-size:9.5px; letter-spacing:0.42em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--vc-oxblood); display:block; margin-bottom:8px;">Received.</strong>
      Thank you. A member of the Council will respond personally — usually within five business days. The center holds.
    </div>

    <div class="newsletter-divider">
      <h4>Stay in the record.</h4>
      <p>Get dispatches from the Coalition — research, program updates, and board intelligence. Twice a month at most.</p>
      <form class="nl-row" data-vc-form data-subject="newsletter-signup" data-endpoint="/api/contact" novalidate>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required autocomplete="email" aria-label="Email for newsletter"/>
        <button type="submit" class="vc-cta-primary" style="white-space:nowrap;">Subscribe →</button>
      </form>
      <p style="font-size:12px; color:var(--vc-muted); margin-top:10px; font-family:var(--vc-text);">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
